name: Hi! I'm Shana Moore
tagline: I'm a Ruby Developer in training!
body:
A few fun facts

I believe in lipstick and dresses, and dessert first(always), and positive vibes only. I'm a military brat, a nerd, a dog lover, and problem-solver, with a little dose of quirk. I try to make my todays better than my yesterdays, without hurting anyone in the process. I am the creator of #thepaintedlipsproject, a Youtube channel, which led me to the journey of building my own website. I accidentally fell in love with coding... oops!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
